A descriptive caption for this image

of a modern multi-story residential building set against a clear evening sky. The building features a sleek, minimalist design with clean lines and a neutral color palette. The facade is predominantly white, with horizontal wooden slats adding texture and warmth to the exterior. The roof is flat, topped with a wooden deck that extends over the front entrance, providing a natural, earthy contrast to the modern architecture. The building consists of four stories, each with large, floor-to-ceiling windows that illuminate the interior spaces with a warm, inviting glow. The first floor includes a spacious entrance area with a glass door, flanked by smaller windows. The second and third floors have multiple windows, some of which are divided into smaller panes, giving the building a more intricate appearance. The ground floor is adorned with a small, neatly manicured lawn, bordered by a low hedge, and a single, slender tree, adding a touch of greenery to the otherwise stark design. The building is situated on a quiet street, with a few neighboring houses visible in the background, adding to the suburban setting.

1、大模型即图库，选择所需图像对应的大模型，必选     2、需要加强某种风格可选择LORA模型，强度可调，可选     3、正反提示词6神提示词插件，可以点击做下角图标6，或者ctrl+q打开提示词编辑界面，有预设、可翻译、可随机灵感   
4、采样器: (1)随机数种子+运行后操作可固定，固定即基本固定图像不变   (2)步数+CFG+采样调度器参考大模型适用，CFG越高越偏向提示词AI发挥空间越小   (3)降噪是重绘幅度，关键参数           5、CLIP文本编码可调提示词权重
